# FILE: home/examsHub/examsHub.desc
# ROLE: High-Urgency Exam Season Command Center
# ROUTE: /exam-hub
# ACCOUNT: All can view — admin-triggered seasonal mode
# THEME: Dark · rose/red alert palette · intensive study mode

## 1. HEADER TRIGGER (Admin-Controlled Signal)
- EXAM SEASON TOGGLE in /admin/config: isExamSeason boolean
- isExamSeason === true:
  - Header "الأخبار" badge → CRITICAL ROSE (#F43F5E) + blinking pulse animation
  - Clicking badge → redirects to /exam-hub
- isExamSeason === false:
  - Badge → normal rose/indigo style · generic news behavior

## 2. HUB PAGE LAYOUT
- PAGE BG: dot-bg + rose radial glow overlay
- HEADER: section-label "موسم الامتحانات" (rose) + h1 gradient-text "مركز القيادة الامتحانية"

## 3. LIVE RESOURCES TERMINAL
- GRID: 3 columns
  - CARD STYLE: bg-[#0F1828] · border-[#F43F5E]/20 · rounded-2xl
  - Content: video tutorials + crash courses with "مباشر" (Live) badge
  - Source: admin-pushed links

## 4. PREDICTED RESOURCES
- One-click download cards for "نماذج امتحانات متوقعة" and Shorts summaries
- Pulls from /library filtered by exam-tagged documents

## 5. STUDY CHAT ROOMS (Future)
- Branch-specific real-time discussion rooms for peer help
- Each room labeled by faculty + year

## 6. EXAM-SPECIFIC OFFERS
- Time-limited discounts on exam-prep courses
- Ad zones: targeted local "مقاهي الدراسة" ads from business advertiser accounts

## 7. ADMIN CONTROL (from /admin/config)
- Master toggle: isExamSeason ON/OFF
- Content management: push live links, predicted files, chat topics
